    LensEventListener<SessionEvent>
    Enclosing class:
    MetricsServiceImpl

    public class MetricsServiceImpl.AsyncSessionEventListener
extends AsyncEventListener<SessionEvent>
    The listener interface for receiving asyncSession events. The class that is interested in processing a asyncSession event implements this interface, and the object created with that class is registered with a component using the component's <code>addAsyncSessionEventListener<code> method. When the asyncSessionEvent event occurs, that object's appropriate method is invoked.
